dText":"Blackmores Deep Sleep Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Deep Sleep Size Size 30 tablets 60 tablets 120 tablets Good health changes everything - support your rest and recovery with Blackmores Deep Sleep. This herbal blend combines valerian, hops, and ziziphus - traditionally used in Chinese and Western herbal medicine to relieve sleeplessness and promote deep, restorative sleep. It’s formulated to enhance sleep quality and help maintain healthy sleeping patterns, while also calming the mind and soothing nervous tension. Valerian is used to reduce the time to fall asleep and support refreshing sleep, while ziziphus has long been recognised for its calming properties. Together, these ingredients help maintain nervous system function and assist mind relaxation. This product offers natural support for quality sleep and general wellbeing. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Sleep Nervous Tension Nervous System Health No Added Wheat No Added Gluten No Added Yeast No Added Soya Bean No Added Dairy Halal Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits Improves sleep quality and supports deep sleep. Relieves restless sleep. Supports waking up refreshed. Helps soothe nerves and calms the mind. Helps mind relaxation. Supports nervous system function. Dosage Adults Take 2 tablets once a day, 30 minutes to an hour before bedtime. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. In rare cases, valerian may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing skin/eyes or unusual: fatigue, nausea, appetite loss, abdominal pain, dark urine or itching. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. May cause drowsiness, if affected do not drive a vehicle or operate machinery. Always talk to your health professional before taking multiple products to support sleep. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Improves sleep quality and supports deep sleep. Relieves restless sleep. Supports waking up refreshed. Helps soothe nerves and calms the mind. Helps mind relaxation. Supports nervous system function. Adults Take 2 tablets once a day, 30 minutes to an hour before bedtime. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. In rare cases, valerian may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing skin/eyes or unusual: fatigue, nausea, appetite loss, abdominal pain, dark urine or itching. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. May cause drowsiness, if affected do not drive a vehicle or operate machinery. Always talk to your health professional before taking multiple products to support sleep. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Magnesium phosphate pentahydrate 363 mg equivalent magnesium 75 mg Ziziphus jujuba var spinosa (ziziphus) extract dry conc. 250 mg equivalent dry seed 5000 mg (5 g) Valeriana officinalis (valerian) extract dry conc. 300 mg equivalent dry root 1200 mg (1.2 g) Humulus lupulus (hops) extract dry conc. 40 mg equivalent dry fruit 200 mg Deep Sleep Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International