 formulation.","descriptionEn":"A blend of probiotics and nutrients to support immune function, intestinal health and general health and well being. Available in fridge free formulation.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Probiotics+ Immune Defence 30s – Immune Support All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Probiotics+ Immune Defence Size Size 30 capsules 90 capsules Blackmores Probiotics+ Immune Defence is a scientifically formulated probiotic with five strains, plus prebiotics, vitamin C and zinc. It helps support healthy immune system function, and relieve symptoms of the common cold. This formula also helps maintain intestinal health, restore beneficial gut flora after antibiotic use, and support healthy gastrointestinal immune function. Conveniently shelf-stable, this formulation supports everyday health and immune defence. Good health changes everything - support your immune system with Probiotics+ Immune Defence. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Gut Flora Immune System Health Common Colds & Flu Digestive Health No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits No need to refrigerate. A potent, multi-action formula containing probiotics and the added benefit of zinc and vitamin C. Reduces the symptoms and duration of colds. Supports healthy immune system function. Supports gastrointestinal health. Helps restore good gut bacteria, including after antibiotic use. Supports general health and wellbeing. Gluten Free. Dosage Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your healthcare professional before use. Adults only. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings No need to refrigerate. A potent, multi-action formula containing probiotics and the added benefit of zinc and vitamin C. Reduces the symptoms and duration of colds. Supports healthy immune system function. Supports gastrointestinal health. Helps restore good gut bacteria, including after antibiotic use. Supports general health and wellbeing. Gluten Free. Adults Take 1 capsule once a day,