 formula developed for kids aged 2+.","descriptionEn":"Blackmores Probiotics+ Kids Daily Health helps children’s gut flora and supports immune system health with a probiotic formula developed for kids aged 2+.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Probiotics+ Kids Daily Health Sachets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Probiotics+ Kids Daily Health Size Size 30 x 1.3g sachets Blackmores Probiotics+ Kids Daily Health is formulated to help maintain immune system health, intestinal health, and general health and wellbeing in children aged 2 years and over. It contains a specific combination of probiotic strains, with added prebiotics and vitamins C and D, to help restore good gut flora after antibiotic use and relieve the severity of common cold symptoms in children over 2 years of age. It also helps restore healthy gut flora, gastrointestinal system health, and healthy immune system function. The formula is conveniently packaged in individual powder sachets to help protect probiotic potency, support freshness, and ensure accurate dosing. With no need for refrigeration, it&#x27;s suitable for busy families and travel. Taken daily, it provides multi-action support for kids’ digestive and immune health. Good health changes everything - nurture your child’s daily wellbeing with Blackmores Probiotics+ Kids Daily Health. Product Format Powder Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Gut Flora Digestive Health Immune System Health No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits 12.5 billion good bacteria plus prebiotic and vitamins. Helps restore good gut flora following the use of antibiotics. Helps reduce the occurrence and severity of common colds in children over 2 years of age. Supports healthy immune system function. No need to refrigerate. Supports general health & wellbeing. No added artificial colours or flavours. Gluten Free. Dosage Children 2 years and over Give the contents of 1 sachet (1.3 g) once a day, or as professionally prescribed. The contents of 1 sachet may be given directly on the tongue, or dissolved in cool water, juice, milk or food and consumed immediately. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Use only under adult supervision. Not to be used in children under two years of age without medical advice. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. If symptoms persist, talk to your health practitioner. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings 12.5 billion good bacteria plus prebiotic and vitamins. Helps restore good gut flora following the use of antibiotics. Helps reduce the occurrence and severity of common colds in children over 2 years of age. Supports healthy immune system function. No need to refrigerate. Supports general health & wellbeing. No added artificial colours or flavours. Gluten Free. Children 2 years and over Give the contents of 1 sachet (1.3 g) once a day, or as professionally prescribed. The contents of 1 sachet may be given directly on the tongue, or dissolved in cool water, juice, milk or food and consumed immediately. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Use only under adult supervision. Not to be used in children under two years of age without medical advice. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. If symptoms persist, talk to your health practitioner. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per 1.3 g sachet: Lactobacillus acidophilus CUL60 5 billion CFU Lactobacillus acidophilus CUL21 5 billion CFU Bifidobacterium bifidum CUL20 125 million CFU Bifidobacterium animalis subsp lactis CUL34 2.375 billion CFU Total good bacteria 12.5 billion CFU Inulin (prebiotic) 100 mg Ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 50 mg Colecalciferol 5 mg equivalent vitamin D3 200 IU 200 IU Probiotics+ Kids Daily Health Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores