 muscle mass, strength, bone health and immune function in older adults.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Muscle Protect Plus All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Muscle Protect Plus Size Size 60 tablets Blackmores Muscle Protect Plus, contains calcium beta-hydroxy-beta-methylbutyrate monohydrate, also known as calcium HMB, as well as vitamin D3 to maintain muscle mass and support muscle function in aging individuals. As muscle mass slowly declines with age, Blackmores created Muscle Protect Plus, with scientific ingredient HMB to help decrease protein breakdown in the muscles and support muscle mass in aging individuals. Vitamin D helps absorption of dietary calcium which supports bone health and bone strength. This formula is designed for adults over 50 seeking enhanced muscle and skeletal health. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Muscle Health Bone Health No Added Wheat No Added Gluten No Added Yeast No Added Dairy Halal Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits Helps in the maintenance of lean body mass in aging individuals. Helps decrease protein breakdown in the muscles in aging individuals. Maintains muscle health and function. Vitamin D helps absorption of dietary calcium which supports bone health and bone strength. A diet deficient in calcium can lead to osteoporosis in later life. Supports healthy immune system function. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet three times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Vitamins can only be of assistance if the dietary vitamin intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Helps in the maintenance of lean body mass in aging individuals. Helps decrease protein breakdown in the muscles in aging individuals. Maintains muscle health and function. Vitamin D helps absorption of dietary calcium which supports bone health and bone strength. A diet deficient in calcium can lead to osteoporosis in later life. Supports healthy immune system function. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet three times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Vitamins can only be of assistance if the dietary vitamin intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Calcium beta-hydroxy-beta-methylbutyrate monohydrate (Calcium HMB as myHMB®) 1000 mg (1 g) Colecalciferol 8.3 micrograms equivalent vitamin D3 333.3 IU Muscle Protect Plus Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Contacts & FAQs Report a Suspected Adverse Experience Contact Us Ask a Naturopa