health and function. This formulation with a well absorbed form of omega-3 and high concentrate DHA plus eye supporting nutrients helps to relieve dry eyes and maintain healthy vision and blood circulation. It can reduce visual fatigue particularly associated with extended screen exposure and as an advanced eye support also supports macula and retina health. Designed for those who are looking to supplement omega-3, Omega + Vision combines omega-3 with essential nutrients lutein, bilberry, and vitamin D to support healthy vision. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Eye Health Macula Health No Added Gluten No Added Yeast No Added Dairy Halal Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits Relieves dry eyes. Helps reduce visual fatigue from prolonged screen use. Supports healthy eye function and vision. Supports eye retina and macula health. Supports vitality. Supports blood vessel and capillary health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Contains omega-3 with high concentrate DHA. Dosage Adults General eye health : Take 1 capsule once a day. Targeted benefits: Take 2 capsules once a day. Do not exceed 2 capsules in 24 hours. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions before use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Relieves dry eyes. Helps reduce visual fatigue from prolonged screen use. Supports healthy eye function and vision. Supports eye retina and macula health. Supports vitality. Supports blood vessel and capillary health. Supports general hea