label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Inflammation Mild Arthritis No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Reduces symptoms of mild osteoarthritis. Relieves inflammation. Non-GMO specialised NZ marine oil extract of green-lipped mussel. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Initially, take 2 capsules 2 times a day for up to 8 weeks. Then reduce dose to 1 capsule two times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Not recommended for people with seafood allergies. If symptoms persist see your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains mollusc, soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Reduces symptoms of mild osteoarthritis. Relieves inflammation. Non-GMO specialised NZ marine oil extract of green-lipped mussel. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Adults Initially, take 2 capsules 2 times a day for up to 8 weeks. Then reduce dose to 1 capsule two times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Not recommended for people with seafood allergies. If symptoms persist see your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains mollusc, soya bean products and sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per capsul