ynthesis. Blackmores Prostate Health Formula supports your wellbeing - because good health changes everything. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Prostate Health Antioxidant for Free Radical Damage No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Supports healthy prostate function. Supports testosterone formation. Helps reduce free radical damage to the body. Dosage Adults Take 2 capsules two times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high dosage. A daily dose of 150 microgram for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Supports healthy prostate function. Supports testosterone formation. Helps reduce free radical damage to the body. Adults Take 2 capsules two times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high dosage. A daily dose of 150 microgram for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Serenoa repens (saw palmetto) extract soft conc. 160 mg equivalent dry fruit 1600 mg (1.6 g) standardise